highFreqInterposerFlow(25.10)                    highFreqInterposerFlow(25.10)

Name
       highFreqInterposerFlow

Syntax
        highFreqInterposerFlow {0 | 1}

       Type: Boolean

       Default: 0

       Specifies  the flow as a high frequency interposer flow. When set to 1,
       setIntegRouteConstraint will auto turn off the options  which  are  not
       suitable for interposer routing.

Related Information
              * setIntegRouteConstraint

